{"tid":2322600,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"32歲DJ Soda着爆乳女僕裝 嘟嘴誘fans","createTime":"2020-12-12T12:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T15:51:44.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"543b68650e3c79bf2379b87c20a89730c62fe94e","tid":2322600,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T12:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hH0WqkQ8JaAvHi2HrfdmeteyTnI=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QOZUVX6WLFARRNH6A7TFX4TD4Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhH0WqkQ8JaAvHi2HrfdmeteyTnI%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQOZUVX6WLFARRNH6A7TFX4TD4Y.jpg&h=23666fa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國DJ界32歲女神DJ Soda，一向性感過人，即使被質疑整容隆胸，她也懶理他人評論，依然故我。<br />\n<br />\nIG逾410萬關注<br />\n<br />\n雖然近日韓國天氣十分寒冷，但DJ Soda亦大派福利，不時在IG晒性感相，令她的IG已有逾410萬的關注人數，人氣十足。而DJ Soda未知是否擔心一眾fans在疫情下長期困在家中而大感鬱結，所以近排她不時搞搞新意思，以不同造型同fans講晚安，繼日前以泳裝look登場後，前日又cosplay做女僕。DJ Soda穿上爆乳女僕裝，戴上淺藍色假髮，拿起茶具嘟嘴同fans道晚安，勁誘fans。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/59ZATLsqegxy8yVDN69Rz3dYhnE=/802x1002/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CWJSDPPM4BH25GIE7KU3MIKDMQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F59ZATLsqegxy8yVDN69Rz3dYhnE%3D%2F802x1002%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCWJSDPPM4BH25GIE7KU3MIKDMQ.jpg&h=7419a117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Fnkhxxdv6OIgw_XW0a7U2hNOQuw=/802x1002/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XAJATRDWQ5ALVEDRN4VJ5QUWLE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFnkhxxdv6OIgw_XW0a7U2hNOQuw%3D%2F802x100